00:46:15.372 --> 00:46:16.830
Yeah, people were
just tremendously

00:46:16.830 --> 00:46:18.960
encouraging to be honest.

00:46:18.960 --> 00:46:19.960
AUDIENCE: I'm surprised.

00:46:19.960 --> 00:46:21.460
LEANNE BROWN: I
know it's very cool.

00:46:21.460 --> 00:46:23.002
GAIL SIMMONS: Have
faith in humanity.

00:46:23.002 --> 00:46:25.376
LEANNE BROWN: Gave me so much
faith in humanity actually,

00:46:25.376 --> 00:46:25.900
