And in a way we can't
do a lot as individuals.

00:46:49.430 --> 00:46:50.810
And that's a fact.

00:46:50.810 --> 00:46:54.540
It's large policy shifts
that will make an impact,

00:46:54.540 --> 00:46:57.030
but we want to help
with these things.

00:46:57.030 --> 00:46:59.280
And so I think supporting
the Kickstarter,

00:46:59.280 --> 00:47:03.510
sort of being able to get this
book out to some more people,

00:47:03.510 --> 00:47:07.520
being able to sort of point to
this as some type of evidence,

00:47:07.520 --> 00:47:10.650
as some sort of piece of hope,
meant a lot to a lot of people.

00:47:10.650 --> 00:47:13.080
And they were willing to
put their money behind it

00:47:13.080 --> 00:47:15.910
and put their confidence behind
it and let more people know,

00:47:15.910 --> 00:47:16.820
so that it spread.

00:47:16.820 --> 00:47:20.730
And to me that just
shows awesome things.

00:47:20.730 --> 00:47:22.230
GAIL SIMMONS: Well,
it's empowering.

00:47:22.230 --> 00:47:25.689
It's empowering for people
